 sight for a company that is being</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/679693512/image_679693512.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742350-amazon-strong-year-but-market-expects-more", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 18:40:43"}, {"id": "4742362", "title": "Momentum, Large-Cap Growth Set To Top Factors Returns In 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business man puts the wooden cube with success icon standing with the success factors; experience, personal, network, relationship, vision. Leader and C-suite reaching concept.\" data-id=\"1383266080\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Khaosai Wongnatthakan/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The winners keep on winning. That sums up the horse race for much of this year based on a set of ETFs targeting the main US equity factor risk premiums. Going into the home stretch for 2024, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383266080/image_1383266080.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742362-momentum-large-cap-growth-set-to-top-factors-returns-in-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 18:35:00"}, {"id": "4742169", "title": "Fluidra: A Robust Pool Equipment Company, But The Stock Isn't Cheap", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pool bottom brush cleaner\" data-id=\"2185583803\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185583803/image_2185583803.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width